# Global configuration section
#   Values here are used as defaults for any following Channel section that
#   doesn't specify them.
Expunge None
Create Both

MaildirStore local
Path ~/data/mail/
Subfolders Verbatim
Trash Trash


IMAPStore HTW
Host imap.htw-berlin.de
User dabrows
PassCmd "pass Email/piotr.dabrowski@htw-berlin.de" 

Channel HTW
Far :HTW:
Near :local:HTW/
Patterns *
Expunge Near
Sync All

IMAPStore Posteo
Host posteo.de
User Piotr.Dabrowski@posteo.net
PassCmd "pass Email/piotr.dabrowski@posteo.de"


Channel Posteo
Far :Posteo:
Near :local:Posteo/
Patterns *
Expunge Near
Sync All

Channel HTW-inbox
Far :HTW:
Near :local:HTW/
Patterns INBOX
Expunge Near
Sync All

Channel Posteo-inbox
Far :Posteo:
Near :local:Posteo/
Patterns INBOX
Expunge Near
Sync All
